data.description: This beautiful raised ranch is located on a corner lot on quiet street close to the hospital, schools and shopping. The yard is spacious and has a shed perfect for storing your outside equipment. There is a fenced in portion off from a large deck. In addition to four bedrooms and three full bathrooms, there is plenty of space with a recreation room, gym, and bonus room. There is a gas fireplace in the recreation room.
